{"tid":533271,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇圖]有冇人知西莎罐頭有冇蟲既成份？","createTime":"2018-01-18T15:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T15:54:22.000Z","uid":85910,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fb6ff494271e4f0a25209a8ce4ebe2368c510175","tid":533271,"uid":85910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T15:07:51.000Z","msg":"間唔時會撈西莎俾屋企隻狗食<br />\n點知撈撈下發現疑似麥皮蟲乾嘅殻<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/18/225650_930f182833c1e2be5e7fa5cd86709fe2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F18%2F225650_930f182833c1e2be5e7fa5cd86709fe2.png&h=f584df11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而背後成份冇寫關於昆蟲或者甲殻動物嘅資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/18/225817_a7ea6ddc33765476937bfa80432b8d07.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F18%2F225817_a7ea6ddc33765476937bfa80432b8d07.png&h=e431346d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後成罐掟落垃圾桶唔想俾佢食<br />\n我知蟲有豐富蛋白質 亦知西莎係垃圾食物<br />\n但冇諗過牛肉及肝會送埋半條蟲俾我<br />\n係我孤陋寡聞定點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78065c8f6b8e6698a35cf5457747ad27ac4a72ad","tid":533271,"uid":766,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T15:08:45.000Z","msg":"狗食條蟲有乜大不了呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1058796c986e2d6f88d7e033cc03aa753516f2","tid":533271,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T15:14:21.000Z","msg":"狗都唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f943bec23d68490e51640765b0c4223b3b00b8f","tid":533271,"uid":85910,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"78065c8f6b8e6698a35cf5457747ad27ac4a72ad","tid":533271,"uid":766,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T15:08:45.000Z","msg":"狗食條蟲有乜大不了呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"